media:group.media:title: Speedrunning Super Mario Bros Underwater
media:group.media:description:
Super Mario Bros is one of the most iconic speedruns of all time, but I wanted to make it more challenging. So today, we're speedrunning it completely underwater

My 2nd channel (WEEKLY UPLOADS): https://www.youtube.com/eaziestspeezy
Watch live at: https://twitch.tv/EazySpeezy

▶ Twitter: https://twitter.com/EazySpeezy
▶ Instagram: https://instagram.com/EazySpeezy/
▶ Merch: https://eazyspeezy.com

Watch the world record speedrun here: this video if you're only counting underwater speedruns
Watch the world record speedrun for above water Super Mario Bros here: https://youtu.be/UY6slAvxQSU
If you want to learn more about fast 4-2, I recommend this video by @Summoning Salt: https://youtu.be/i1AHCaokqhg

My channel generally focuses on a more casual side of speedruns. With these videos I want to show off cool speedruns, explain how they work, and entertain. Hopefully you enjoy the content and maybe even take up speedrunning yourself, because it is truly a lot of fun!
